{
  "chapter": 95,
  "chapter_summary": "第九十五回 阴险毒辣。苏樱与花无缺对话后离去，花无缺独自离开寻找出路。小鱼儿与胡药师、江玉郎、铁萍姑等待苏樱未果，江玉郎以花无缺安危相要挟，提出以女儿红毒菌换取小鱼儿服毒的条件。小鱼儿明知危险仍吞下女儿红，江玉郎随后带众人前往藏匿花无缺的洞穴。到达山壁洞穴后，江玉郎突然将小鱼儿推入深洞，露出真面目——此前的病弱伪装全是骗局。江玉郎又将胡药师踢下洞穴，与铁萍姑纠缠之际，一名戴木面具的白衣神秘人突然出现，轻易将铁萍姑抛上高树，一袖拂回江玉郎的拳头。白衣人疑似移花宫高手，江玉郎惊恐跪地求饶。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "和你关在一起的那个人，叫江玉郎，你认不认得他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我但愿不认得他才好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你为什么不杀了他呢！留这个人活在世上，实在是后患无穷。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他此刻既伤且病，我怎能向他出手？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "这就是君子的毛病，但你若没有这毛病，我只怕也……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "等一等，我还有句话要告诉你。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "什么话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "铁心兰并没有看错，你实在是个温柔又可爱的男人，也实在对她好得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "你算准苏樱一定能找到这里来么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "胡药师",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "胡药师",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "在下中的毒，只怕快发作了吧？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "你，苏樱若不来，我再也不会为你解毒的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "胡药师",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "苏姑娘是否前来，和在下又有何关系？你下的毒若是发作了……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "毒性发作了，算你倒霉，你死了也活该，谁叫你说苏樱一定会来的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "走，不管她来不来，咱们先去找她去。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "现在若先去找苏姑娘，再转回来救花公子，花公子只怕已……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "只怕已怎样？说！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "实不相瞒，我藏起花无缺的那地方，并不太舒服，而且有点不大透气，时间若是隔得太长，说不定会闷死人的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "江兄是聪明人，总该知道花无缺若死了，对江兄你也没什么好处。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这个小弟自然明白的，只不过……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你救了他，我负责要苏樱将解药给你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小弟现在已想通了，只觉世情皆是虚幻，生生死死，也只不过是一场梦而已，是否能拿到解药，小弟实已不放在心上。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你……你真的是江玉郎么？妙极妙极，江兄原来是个老和尚投胎转世的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小弟虽已不再将这副臭皮囊放在心上，只不过……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "只不过她……她对我的恩情，却令我再也抛不开，放不下。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小弟经此一劫，再也无意与诸兄逐鹿江湖，只盼将恩仇俱一刀斩断，和她寻个山林隐处，安安分分的度此余年，可是……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "可是小弟虽有此意，怎奈以前做的错事实在太多，小弟也自知鱼兄绝不会就此放过我的，是么？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "常言道：放下屠刀，立地成佛。江兄如此做法，小弟佩服还来不及，又怎么会再找江兄的麻烦呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "鱼兄博闻广见，想必知道野生蕈菌中有一种叫女儿红的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这女儿红又是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "这女儿红乃是生在极阴湿之地的一种毒菌，据说无论谁吃了，不出三五天，就会得一种怪病。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "什么怪病？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "这种病开始时也没什么，只觉不过有些晕晕欲睡，精神恍惚，就好像得了相思病似的，除非每隔几个月，能找到一株'恶婆草'连根吃下去，否则这相思病就要越来越重，不出一年，就完蛋大吉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "此时此刻，江兄忽然提起此物来，难道是想要小弟也害一害这相思病么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "这么珍贵的东西，一时之间，你能到哪里去找来给我吃？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小弟若是去别处寻找，就算找个三年五载，也未必能找得到，但凑巧的是，这附近就偏偏有一株，只要鱼兄答应，小弟立刻就可去为鱼兄掘来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你疯了么？怎么能说得出这种话？他……他怎么可能答应你？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "鱼兄想必知道，那恶婆草虽也和女儿红一样，十分稀罕珍贵，但却可以用人工来培养的，而小弟又恰巧知道培养它的法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这里的事办完之后，小弟就立刻找个地方隐居起来，专心为鱼兄培植恶婆草，鱼兄若想身体健康，自然也就会好生保护小弟的性命了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "胡药师",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你难道以为小鱼儿是呆子么？这种事你就算杀了我，我也不会答应的，何况这条比泥鳅还滑溜的小鱼儿？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你信不过我，我又怎信得过你？我怎知道你会为我培植恶婆草，又怎知这恶婆草一定能吃到嘴呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小弟的病毒也一直不解，鱼兄要杀我，还是容易得很。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "但我若找不到你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "鱼兄若真的要找，小弟就算上天入地，也躲不了的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "我吃下了这女儿红，你就去救花无缺？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小弟若是失言背信，鱼兄随时都可要小弟的命。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "好，我答应你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "胡药师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "疯子，疯子，这人原来是疯子，别人说太聪明的人，有时往往会变成疯子，这话听来倒是一点也不错。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妙极妙极，想不到这女儿红竟是人间第一美味，我这一辈子，简直没有吃过这么鲜嫩的东西。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "绝代之佳人，大多是倾国倾城的祸水，致命之毒物，也常常是人间美味，惟有良药，才是苦口的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "好听的话，大多是骗人的，江兄还是少说两句，赶紧去救人吧！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "那地方究竟是哪里，你说出来，我抱你去。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "如此劳动鱼兄，小弟怎么敢当。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "没关系，你骨头轻得很，我抱你并不费力。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "求求你们两个人，莫要再斗嘴了好不好？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我怎敢跟鱼兄斗嘴，只不过……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "鱼兄可瞧见上面那洞穴么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这地方还不错吧！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你为什么不用块石头将洞口堵上呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "花公子现在已是寸步难行，小弟反正也不怕他逃走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "洞口既没有堵上，他怎么会闷死？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "也许不会被闷死，但荒山上的洞穴里，总难免有些毒蛇恶兽……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "鱼兄不妨先将小弟放下来，看看这地方对不对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "花公子，小弟等来救你了，你听得见么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "花公子，你……你……你怎么样了，怎地……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "鱼兄，可瞧见花公子了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你这小子究竟在玩什么花样，为什么……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "鱼兄……小鱼儿……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小鱼儿……小鱼儿，你毕竟还是不如我江玉郎，毕竟还是上了我的当了！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你将小鱼儿怎么样？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "我不害死他，难道还等他害死我么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你不是已改过了么？不是只想和我安度余生，怎地又……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "胡药师",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "小鱼儿既已中了女儿红的毒，你以后岂非正可以此要挟他，要他乖乖地听命于你，你现在就害死了他，岂非可惜？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "你想不通，小鱼儿也想不通的，所以他才会上当。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "方才那女儿红只不过是个钩子而已，你现在可想通了么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小鱼儿呀小鱼儿，你常常自命自己是天下第一个聪明人，如此你总该知道，天下第一个聪明人，到底是谁了吧？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "胡药师",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "但花无缺呢？他难道也被你害死了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "你以为花无缺很呆板么？告诉你，他也会骗人的，他故意装出那副痴痴呆呆的模样，让你们不再提防他，他却乘机溜之大吉。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "胡药师",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "那么，白山君呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "那时我病发作得厉害，迷迷糊糊的，也没有瞧清楚，好像是瞧见他去追花无缺了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "胡药师",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "不好，我中的毒药力还未消散，我还得找他要解药。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "很好，你就下去找他吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "好个兔二爷，果然有两下子！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "方才我出的那几脚，你可瞧见了么？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "瞧见了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "那是北派谭腿中的精华'卧鱼八式'，和胡家堡的'无影脚'，武当派的'流星步'，饱宝派的'飞龙式'，四种武林绝技混合在一起变化而成的。我替它取了个名字，叫'踢死人不赔命，天下无双魔脚'，你说妙不妙？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "妙极了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你有个武功如此高明的夫婿，难道不高兴么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你这是干什么？咱们已有很久没在一起，现在我的病已好了，咱们正可以好好的温存温存，你为什么不理我？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你还是找别人温存去吧，像你这样既聪明，武功义高的大英雄，大豪杰，我怎么高攀得上！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "我去找别人？去找谁？我喜欢的只有你呀！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你……你……你放不放手？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "我不放手，我偏不放手，你打死我，我也舍不得放手的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你先放手，我问你一句话。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你问呀，我又没有堵住你的嘴！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "我问你，你害死了小鱼儿，难道还不过瘾，为何又要害死胡药师？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "我看见那小子对你色迷迷的模样，简直快气疯了，恨不得当时就宰了他。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你……你杀他，难道是为了我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "也不知为了什么，只要别人瞧你一眼，我就气得要死，何况他居然想打你的主意……除了我之外，谁敢动你一根手指，我拼命也要宰了他的。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "不行，不可以在这里……",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "这里连鬼都没有一个，有谁会瞧见，来吧……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "快跳下来，我接住你。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "你这人有什么毛病，好生生的为何来找我的麻烦？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "你……你莫非就是移花宫主？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "凭你这样的人，也配说'移花宫主'四个字？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren",
      "text": "小人的确不配说这四个字，小人该打。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 95,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    }
  ],
